---
const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<section class="relative text-white overflow-hidden min-h-[600px] md:min-h-[700px]">
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img src={`${base}images/subsidy/hero.jpg`} alt="窓際で過ごす家族" class="w-full h-full object-cover" width="1477" height="1108" fetchpriority="high" />
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-900/60 to-transparent"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-24 md:py-36">
    <div class="max-w-lg">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6 animate-fade-in-up">
        補助金で、窓から<br />暮らしの質を上げる。
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-white/90 mb-10 animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-100">
        補助金を活用した窓リフォームで、<br />今の暮らしに合った、無理のない整え方を。
      </p>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 animate-fade-in-up animate-delay-200">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-full w-28 h-28 flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
          <span class="text-primary-600 text-[10px] font-bold">先進的窓リノベ2026</span>
          <span class="text-primary-600 text-xs">最大</span>
          <span class="text-primary-600 text-2xl font-bold leading-none">200<span class="text-sm">万円</span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-full w-28 h-28 flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
          <span class="text-primary-600 text-lg font-bold">見積無料</span>
          <span class="text-primary-600 text-[10px]">しつこい営業は行いません！</span>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-full w-28 h-28 flex flex-col items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
          <span class="text-primary-600 text-sm font-bold">神戸市</span>
          <span class="text-primary-600 text-sm font-bold">全域に対応</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
